    "The authors also reported using ChatGPT as an aid for prompt engineering to arrive at the final prompt used to compare different LLMs, including Google Bard.",
    "Such use of LLMs to aid in using other LLMs is likely to rise in the future.",
    "LLMs for Combating Health MisinformationThe rapid spread of misinformation through social media is an active topic of concern among the broader healthcare community [101].",
